  {{else}}
  <p>
    For us to be able to process and make a decision about your application as quickly as possible, we need to understand your current financial position and likely funding gap over the next six months. We recommend that you spend some time reviewing your finances and once you are in a position to answer this question, go through this assessment again.
  </p>
  {{/ifAll ~}}
  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TRSF is not the right fund for you. This fund is to help charities and organisations to stabilise cashflow issues during this difficult period. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding/for-organisations">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>.
  </p>
