  </p>
  {{/if ~}}
  {{else}}
  <p>
    We are sorry but the TSRF is not the right fund for you. This fund is for registered charities, voluntary organisations and social enterprises only. You may be eligible for other funding, <a href="/support/coronavirus/funding/for-organisations">find out more about other COVID-19 emergency funds</a>.
  </p>
